oposition, HLB is positioning itself to capture the rapidly evolving wealth flows across Asia, transforming traditional asset management into a vibrant, holistic ecosystem for a modern, global clientele. According to Andrew Jong, HLB's Managing Director of Personal Financial Services, \"Our transformation plan is built on anticipating where the future of banking is headed, and wealth management sits at the very heart of that growth strategy. The new generation of ultra-high-net-worth individuals doesn't just look for asset preservation. They demand sophisticated, borderless solutions that match their multifaceted lives, and this invite-only card provides access to a highly curated world that mirrors their ambition, global mobility, and taste.\" Establishing itself on the Visa Infinite Privilege tier, the card unlocks a bespoke ecosystem of global privileges centered on high-end travel, master-class gastronomy, and holistic well-being. Invited clients will enjoy rare access to elite global private members' clubs, highly coveted culinary table experiences, and tailored wellness retreats worldwide. About Hong Leong Bank Berhad Please visit www.hlb.com.my", "content": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "keywords": ["debuts", "hong leong bank", "visa infinite privilege card"], "creator": null, "language": "english", "country": ["bhutan", "laos", "yemen", "china", "brunei", "pakistan", "hong kong", "turkmenistan", "afghanistan", "turkey", "macau", "armenia", "singapore", "syria", "bangladesh", "timor-leste", "taiwan", "romania", "azerbaijan", "saudi arabia", "qatar", "india", "united arab emirates", "philippines", "uzbekistan", "tajikistan", "vietnam", "bahrain"], "category": ["business", "top"], "datatype": "pressrelease", "pubDate": "2026-07-17 09:04:00", "pubDateTZ": "UTC", "fetched_at": "2026-07-17 09:23:28", "image_url": "https://mma.prnasia.com/media2/3006505/Andrew_Jong.jpg?p=medium600", "video_url": null, "source_id": "en_prnasisa", "source_name": "Pr Newswire Apac",